#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "More Survivor Notes"
msgstr "更多幸存者筆記"

#. ~ Description for More Survivor Notes
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds more survivor notes for hints for new players."
msgstr "為新手提示添加更多幸存者筆記。"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Killed my best friend yesterday, I can't beleive the world has come to "
"this.\""
msgstr "\"昨天殺了我最好的朋友，我無法相信世界會變成這樣。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Lindsay, meet us at Jason's house. Jason, the nut that he is, is going to "
"set it on fire at midnight before we all make a break for it. He's convinced"
" the monsters aren't afraid of fire, but DRAWN to it. If it works it's at "
"least going to make one giant distraction. Let's hope it'll clear the entire"
" block.\""
msgstr ""
"\"琳賽，到傑森家跟我們碰頭。傑森那個瘋子打算在午夜放火燒房子，然後我們一起突圍。他堅信那些怪物不怕火，反而會被火光吸引。如果這招管用，至少能製造一場巨大的騷亂。但願能把整個街區都清空。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Jason, get all the dryfood out of the kitchen before you... burn "
"everything. And stuff your belly full of anything that's going to go bad "
"soon. -Mom\""
msgstr "\"傑森，在你……燒光一切之前，把廚房裡所有乾貨都拿出來。把快變質的東西都塞進肚子裡吃飽。-媽媽\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"...and remember: Do the math. Your life depends on it. If you have 30 "
"rounds in a rifle, you can take down maybe 10 zombies with it if you're a "
"good shot... and lucky. Can you kill one of those things with 3 rounds?\""
msgstr "\"……記住：算好賬。你的命就靠它了。如果你步槍裡有30發子彈，槍法好又走運的話，大概能放倒10個殭屍……你能用3發子彈幹掉其中一個嗎？\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Dad said something about a bear trap and a tear gas grenade. I... I think "
"he's going to trap and gas that freak moose out on the street. It'll give us"
" meat for weeks if we use the dehydrator. He hasn't come back though...\""
msgstr "\"爸爸提到了捕熊夾和催淚彈。我……我覺得他打算在街上設陷阱用毒氣對付那隻怪駝鹿。如果用脫水機處理，夠我們吃好幾周肉。但他還沒回來……\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Honey, we're going to hole up in the garage for a day before we make a "
"break for it out of the city. If we try to plow through the horde, I fear "
"the car won't stand ten seconds. I'm going to move the engine to the back, "
"and maybe the fuel tank too... add some plating to the front... Maybe "
"reinforce the windows. The modifications are going to take at least a day. "
"Find my caffeine pills. I may not get any sleep in the next 36 hours.\""
msgstr ""
"\"親愛的，我們準備在車庫裡躲一天再突圍出城。如果硬闖屍群，我怕車子撐不過十秒。我打算把引擎移到後面，油箱可能也得挪……前面加裝護板……或許再加固車窗。改裝至少需要一天。找到我的咖啡因藥片，接下來36小時我可能沒法閤眼。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Remember to carry some desinfectant. I ran out, a lighter and a knife had "
"to do in a pinch.\""
msgstr "\"記得帶些消毒劑。我用完了，緊急情況下只能用打火機和刀子湊合。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"[Part of the note is unintelligible] ... I believe these things can't see "
"well at night either. If you're quiet you might just pass a horde.\""
msgstr "\"[部分字跡難以辨認]……我覺得這些東西晚上視力也不好。只要你保持安靜，說不定能悄悄穿過屍群。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"I doubt they can smell anything if you light some tires on fire\""
msgstr "\"要是點著幾個輪胎，我懷疑它們就聞不到氣味了\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Remember when I told you about that moose coming right at me last year? "
"Try shouting at them\""
msgstr "\"還記得我去年說駝鹿直衝我來的事嗎？試試對它們大喊\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Look, I know they look like kids, but you gotta take 'em out. You'll get "
"used to it, just like I have. Remember, those things aren't human anymore.\""
msgstr "\"聽著，我知道它們看起來像孩子，但你必須幹掉它們。你會習慣的，就像我一樣。記住，那些東西已經不是人類了。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Always plan ahead, never sleep in a place that has only one exit. Lost a "
"good friend to a bad decision.\""
msgstr "\"永遠要提前計劃，絕不在只有一個出口的地方睡覺。一個錯誤決定讓我失去了好朋友。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"If you're planning on using a building for a temporary stash, might be a "
"good idea to open and close the windows. Sure, having unlocked windows might"
" seem unsafe, but if I'm trying to sneak back in while some Zed's are "
"wandering near the door, you'll thank me later for the quiet entrance.\""
msgstr ""
"\"如果你打算用建築物當臨時藏匿點，最好先開關幾次窗戶。當然，不鎖窗可能看起來不安全，但如果我想趁殭屍在門口徘徊時溜回來，你會感謝我留了這個安靜入口。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'Mama always used to say life was like a box of chocolates, "
"sometimes it gives you radiation poisoning.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'媽媽總說生活就像一盒巧克力，有時它會給你輻射中毒。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I don't know if we each have a destiny, or if we're all just "
"floatin' around accidental-like on a breeze, but I, I think maybe it's both."
" Maybe both is happenin' at the same time. I mid'ha ate too many of them "
"hallucina'gan mushroms.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'我不知道我們是否各有天命，還是都像隨風飄蕩的偶然，但我，我覺得可能兩者都是。也許兩者同時發生。我可能吃了太多致幻蘑菇。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I swear I am not drunk, but I just saw a bear riding a "
"motorcycle.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'我發誓我沒醉，但我剛看見一隻熊騎著摩托車。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'Heard noises outside.  Saw giant scrapheap move by.  Not going "
"out, nope, never.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'聽到外面有動靜。看見巨型廢料堆移動過去。不出門，絕不，永遠不。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I thought it was a zombie, but there was this thing in the "
"distance, looked like nothing but metal parts stuck together.  A zombie "
"attacked it and it spewed lightning all over, then sprouted blades and "
"minced it.  Not going out, nuh uh.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'我以為是殭屍，但遠處有個東西，看起來就是金屬零件拼湊的。殭屍攻擊它時，它噴出閃電，然後彈出刀刃把殭屍切碎了。不出門，絕對不。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "It reads 'Why are their so many fucking giant spiders?'"
msgstr "上面寫著'為什麼他媽的有這麼多巨型蜘蛛？'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "It reads 'Partake of the fruit, eat the seed, accept the sap'"
msgstr "上面寫著'分享果實，吞食種子，接納汁液'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I saw a rock moving, I took out my blood draw kit then drew blood "
"from it.  Fuck you Vicesimus Knox!'"
msgstr "上面寫著'我看見石頭在動，拿出採血工具給它抽了血。去你媽的維塞西姆斯·諾克斯！'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I knew I shoulda killed that spider in the basement.  Now there is"
" a mob of giant spiders.  Fuck this place.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'早知道該殺了地下室那隻蜘蛛。現在冒出一大群巨型蜘蛛。這鬼地方真他媽操蛋。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "It reads 'Do not go in the fucking basement my dude.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'別他媽進地下室，兄弟。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "It reads 'It reads 'Call me at: 0406 650 430''"
msgstr "上面寫著'上面寫著'打電話給我：0406 650 430''"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "It reads 'Fuck, I don't think this bug spray is going to work.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'操，我覺得這殺蟲劑不管用。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'Those spores don't burn, but the rest of the mushrooms sure as "
"Hell do.'"
msgstr "上面寫著'那些孢子燒不著，但其他蘑菇他媽的一燒就著。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I saw some naked guy try to fistfight a hulk the other day. He "
"died, but someone who looked EXACTLY like him came by 5 minutes later "
"attempting the same exact thing. What the hell's going on there?'"
msgstr "上面寫著'前幾天我看見個裸男想和巨人拳擊。他死了，但五分鐘後來了個長得一模一樣的人做同樣的事。這他媽怎麼回事？'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'If by all laws of aviation a normal bee shouldn’t be able to fly, "
"then how the fuck does a giant one?'"
msgstr "上面寫著'如果按所有航空定律普通蜜蜂都飛不起來，那巨型蜜蜂他媽是怎麼飛的？'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'There was a turret on the corner yesterday.  I watched fifty "
"people who looked the same run right up to it yelling \"SHOOT ME BITCH!\" "
"before the last one punched it and died when it exploded.  Not five minutes "
"later, another ran through the intersection like he knew it was safe.'"
msgstr ""
"上面寫著'昨天拐角有個炮塔。我看著五十個長得一樣的人衝過去喊\"射我啊賤人！\"，最後一個打了它一拳，爆炸時死了。不到五分鐘，又一個穿過路口，好像知道安全了。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I keep having the same dream over and over: here I am slaughtering"
" this electrified zombie, heaps of flesh gouged out, putrified goo and parts"
" filling my hands, slopping against my clothes and face. I can feel the "
"sweat pouring down my cheeks and my back, and every time I pull out some "
"sort of burnt out bionic. Sometimes I find a battery, or if I'm really "
"lucky, I'll find some really extravagant gizmo and I wake up from the "
"dream.'"
msgstr ""
"上面寫著'我反覆做同一個夢：我在屠殺帶電殭屍，大塊血肉被挖出，腐爛黏液和零件沾滿雙手，濺到衣服和臉上。能感覺到汗水順著臉頰和後背流淌，每次都會掏出某種燒壞的仿生部件。有時找到電池，運氣好時能找到特別精巧的裝置，然後就從夢中驚醒。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "It reads 'My mama always used to says \"stupid is as stupid does.\"'"
msgstr "上面寫著'我媽媽總說\"傻人有傻福\"。'"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'There was a man who I met today, he told me his name was Forest.  "
"He talked funny, just after we got acquainted a group of people on bikes "
"came by and he started a' runnin'.  I don't know why but I got this urge to "
"yell, so I did. I yelled \"Run Forest! Run!\" at the top of my lungs.  Just "
"then after I finished yellin' I saw one of them pull out a rifle of sorts "
"and shoot his right in the ass, I heard him yell \"Somethin' dun' jumped up "
"and bit me!\".  That was the last I saw of that man, but to this day if I "
"ever see someone a runnin' I get up and shout \"Run Forest! Run!\" like "
"something just comes over me...' [There seems to be more writing but the "
"rest of the paper is shredded]"
msgstr ""
"上面寫著：‘今天我遇到一個人，他告訴我他叫福雷斯特。他說話怪怪的，我們剛認識就有一群騎自行車的人經過，然後他就開始跑起來。不知為何，我有一股衝動想喊出來，於是我就喊了。我扯著嗓子大喊“快跑，福雷斯特！快跑！”。就在我喊完的那一刻，我看到其中一個人掏出一把步槍之類的槍，正好打中了他的屁股，我聽到他大喊“有什麼東西跳起來咬了我一口！”。那是我最後一次見到那個人，但直到今天，每當我看到有人在奔跑，我就會站起來大喊“快跑，福雷斯特！快跑！”，就像有什麼東西突然控制了我一樣……’"
" [似乎還有更多內容，但紙張的其餘部分被撕碎了]"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I was a chattin' with a man a whiles ago, he was a nic-a person.  "
"Then these people on bikes came and chased after me, I rans and rans but "
"then I felt somethin' a jump up and bite me, I yelled about it to. That nic "
"man was rootin for me-I think. He'd a yell \"Run Forest! Run, and never stop"
" a-runnin\". ' [It seems like a page out of a diary, but the rest "
"unlegible.]"
msgstr ""
"上面寫著：‘不久前我和一個人聊天，他是個好人。然後這些騎自行車的人來了，開始追我，我跑啊跑，但感覺有什麼東西跳起來咬了我一口，我也為此大喊起來。那個好人似乎在為我加油——我想是的。他會大喊“快跑，福雷斯特！快跑，永遠別停下奔跑”。’"
" [這看起來像是日記的一頁，但其餘部分難以辨認。]"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'I used to be in the army.  The Army was real easy. You just have "
"to stand up straight, make your bed real neat, and always answer every "
"question with \"Yes, Drill Seargent!\".'"
msgstr "上面寫著：‘我以前在軍隊待過。軍隊生活真的很簡單。你只需要站得筆直，把床鋪整理得整整齊齊，並且每次回答問題都要說“是，教官！”。’"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It reads 'There was a man, he was protestin' this war with China.  He'd "
"always be yellin' and-a using the \"F\" word, and every time he did a crowd "
"of people would whistle and a-clap for him.'"
msgstr "上面寫著：‘有一個人，他在抗議這場與中國的戰爭。他總是大喊大叫，還滿口“F”字眼，每次他這樣做，都會有一群人吹口哨併為他鼓掌。’"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It seems to be half of a diary entry. It reads '... But in the army we were "
"always takin' long walks and we were always lookin' for a guy named "
"Charlie?'"
msgstr "這似乎是日記的一半。上面寫著：‘……但在軍隊裡，我們總是長途跋涉，而且總是在找一個叫查理的人？’"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It seems to be a diary entry. It reads 'When I joined the army I had to get "
"up on this a-bus, I walked up to the driver and said \"My name'sa Forrest "
"Gump!\". He said to me in a loud voice, \"Nobody gives a hunky shit who you "
"are, pus ball. You're not even a low-life, scum-sucking maggot. Get your ass"
" on the bus, you're in the army now!\" He was a nice man, he always yelled a"
" lot thoug.'"
msgstr ""
"這似乎是一篇日記。上面寫著：‘當我參軍時，我不得不登上這輛巴士，我走到司機面前說“我叫福雷斯特·甘普！”。他大聲對我說，“沒人在乎你他媽的是誰，膿包。你連個低等、吸食渣滓的蛆蟲都不如。滾上車，你現在是軍隊的人了！”。他是個好人，雖然總是大喊大叫。’"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"It seems to be a diary entry. It reads 'In the army I used to have a friend "
"named Bubba, he wanted to be a shrimp boat captian.  Instead he died right "
"there by the ocean over in China'"
msgstr "這似乎是一篇日記。上面寫著：‘在軍隊裡，我曾經有個朋友叫巴布，他想成為一名捕蝦船船長。結果他死在了中國那邊的海邊。’"
